snippet.title: WES Barker
snippet.description:
Magic Tricks
Comedy Sketches. 
Random Ideas

Comedy and Magic come first. Don't take anything too serious. Never blame the beers.

Hosts of BOTTOM OF THE BARREL with Chris Ramsay and Wes Barker
(Some say the greatest Podcast in the World)

Sketches featuring my hilarious wife (Kristen Gillett). Check out her channel too.

Wes Barker...Fooler on Penn & Teller: Fool Us. As seen on America's Got Talent, MTV Greatest Party Stories Ever, Netflix, Amazon Prime, and Wizard Wars.

Follow me @stuntmagician
Find out everything at wesbarker.ca
